Class AV.Cloud.BeforeDeleteResponse

A Response object that is passed to the beforeDelete function. This object contains functions to tell the AV.Cloud what to do with the delete. Available in Cloud Code only.
Defined in: cloud.js.

Class Summary
Constructor Attributes Constructor Name and Description
 
AV.Cloud.BeforeDeleteResponse()
Field Summary
Field Attributes Field Name and Description
 
error
If called, will reject the delete.
 
success
If called, will allow the delete to happen.
Class Detail
AV.Cloud.BeforeDeleteResponse()
Field Detail
{Function} error
If called, will reject the delete. An optional error message may be passed in.
{Function} success
If called, will allow the delete to happen. If a AV.Object is passed in, then the passed in object will be deleted instead.
